

Spring 3 has various view resolvers.
> BeanNameViewResolver. 
> InternalResourceViewResolver
> FreeMarkerViewResolver
> ResourceBundleViewResolver (I18n features ) 
> TilesViewResolver
> URLBasedViewResolver
> ContentNegotiatgionViewResolver ( JSP/ XML / JSON )
WE can have multiple viewresolvers in a single application. 


Spring Tags: 

2 types of form tags we have: 
> spring-tld tags
> spring-form tld tags

Spring TLD tags:
Bind, escapeBody, hasBindErrors, message, nestedPath, theme, transform , URL, eval.

Spring-Form tags:
checkbox, checkboxes, errors, form, hidden, input , label, form , option, password, select .

